 6z\"></path></svg></a>Other useful libraries</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://opauth.org/\">Opauth</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"frameworks\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#frameworks\" aria-label=\"frameworks permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Frameworks</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://flourishlib.com/\">Flourish</a>: Modular</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.symfony-project.org/\">Symfoni</a>: Modular.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://auraphp.github.com/\">Aurora PHP</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"articles\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#articles\" aria-label=\"articles permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Articles</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://marcelog.github.com/articles/ci_jenkins_hudson_continuous_integration_php_phing.html\">PHP Continuous integration, with Jenkins and Phing</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://bradley-holt.com/2011/07/exploring-rabbitmq-and-php/\">Exploring RabbitMQ and PHP</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://cakephp.org/\">CakePHP</a></li>\n</ul>","excerpt":"I started hack